
Dojo Sensor is a dojo module designed to allow developers to access device interfaces which allow web applications to utilize environmental data on a device.  At the present there are three specific modules within Dojo Sensor: geolocation, accelerometer, and media capture.  More information on these modules can be viewed in the documentation.


Installation procedure:

To install simply copy the contents of the src folder into the root directory of a dojo install.  To use just implement it as you would any other dojo module.

Documentation:
http://documentation.innobdesign.com